PrecisOrder authorizing (a) the Treasury Board to act on all matters relating to the development, establishment and administration of a DENTAL SERVICES PLAN or program for all or any pensioners, (b) the President of the Treasury Board to exercise the powers, duties and functions of the Board in that regard during intervals between meetings of the Board, and (c) to enter into contracts with an eligible pensioner in connection therewith.
